Package Model

Class Patient

java.lang.Object
Model.Patient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Patient extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a patient in the hospital management system.

The Patient class contains the patient's personal information, medical history, and associated appointments.

This class implements Serializable to allow patient data to be serialized for persistence.

Since:
2024-11-17
